rows.label: qst200207_msg0002
rows.name:
What is it, so suddenly?
Who on earth are you?

rows.label: qst200207_msg0003
rows.name:
I'm not a suspicious person.
I just want to ask a little bit.

rows.label: qst200207_msg0004
rows.name:
Hmph. The guy who says he isn't
suspicious is the most suspicious.

rows.label: qst200207_msg0005
rows.name:
If you're a debt collector, go home.
We don't have any money to pay back!

rows.label: qst200207_msg0006
rows.name:
Or do you intend to kill me
and take the house and everything!?

rows.label: qst200207_msg0007
rows.name:
I won't do such a thing. I just want
you to tell me about Harghal.

rows.label: qst200207_msg0008
rows.name:
Hah! I don't know anything
about a dissipated daughter like that!

rows.label: qst200207_msg0010
rows.name:
She doesn't know her mother's feelings,
she's truly a selfish daughter!

rows.label: qst200207_msg0011
rows.name: Aren't you worried about your daughter?

rows.label: qst200207_msg0013
rows.name:
What would a total stranger like you
understand about us!
